sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    box rgb(230, 126, 34) Customer
        participant Cust as Customer (Yves)
    end
    box rgb(41, 128, 185) Spryker
        participant Checkout as Checkout / Payment (direct Payone module)
        participant OMS as OMS / StateMachine
        participant RMQ as RabbitMQ (MessageBroker)
    end
    box rgb(39, 174, 96) PSP
        participant Payone as Payone PSP
    end

    Note over Cust: ADR-001 — direct Payone module (ACP is being sunset), not the ACP app
    Cust->>Checkout: Submit checkout (selected Payone method)
    Checkout->>Payone: Pre-authorize / init payment [REST]
    Payone-->>Checkout: PaymentID + redirect URL
    Checkout-->>Cust: Redirect to Payone (iframe/redirect)
    Cust->>Payone: Enter payment details
    Payone-->>Cust: Redirect back to shop (result)
    Checkout->>OMS: Place order (state: new / payment pending)

    Note over Payone,RMQ: Async capture/status via MessageBroker-based event bus
    Payone->>RMQ: Payment status event (authorized / captured / failed)
    RMQ->>OMS: triggerEvent("capture successful")
    OMS->>OMS: Run OMS command (mark paid),<br/>fire-and-forget; retries if command throws
    Note over OMS: 4000-6000 payment messages/day; COINs handled as OMS transitions
